          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections for the production of Li and Be",
                "isotopes in carbon targets irradiated by 300 GeV",
                "protons"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "G.M.Raisbeck",
                "J.Lestringuez",
                "F.Yiou"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,PL/B,57,186,1975",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,PL/B,57,186,1975",
                    "doi": "10.1016/0370-2693(75)90021-0",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "PL/B",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "57",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "186"
                      },
                      "date": 1975
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "#doi:10.1016/0370-2693(75)90021-0"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "2FR CSN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "SYNCH"
                ],
                "institute": "1USANAL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " FNAL accelerator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The proton energy was always 300 GeV except for a",
                "period representing ~5% of the flux of the second",
                "irradiation, in which it was 400 GeV. On the basis of",
                "what follows, we do not believe this significantly",
                "effects our results."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets consisted of eight layers of graphite",
                " (48x40x1 mm), wrapped in A1 foil. Before irradiation",
                "the graphite was heated to ~2500 C for 30 seconds",
                "under an argon atmosphere to ensure that the Li and",
                "Be content were less than 10**-13 g/g."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV",
                "MASSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiations were carried out",
                "parasitically in the neutrino beam line of the FNAL",
                "accelerator several inches in front of the main",
                "production target. Two irradiations were performed,",
                "lasting 45 and 60 days, and receiving total",
                "integrated fluxes of ~3x10**17 and ~1x10**18 protons",
                "respectively. Several weeks after irradiation the",
                "targets were returned to our laboratory for analysis.",
                "Cross sections for the production of Li and Be",
                "isotopes in carbon targets irradiated by 300 GeV",
                "protons have been measured by mass spectrometry."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Estimated experimental uncertainties."
